text.div:
• Include these codes as defined in http://smart.who.int/ig/smart-immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZ.D
    CodeDisplayDefinition
    DE2CompletedThe immunization event was successfully carried out as intended
    DE3Entered in errorImmunization event record has been mistakenly created or entered into system. Recorded information is incorrect or should not have been documented, though it is possible that real-world decisions were based on it
    DE4Not donePlanned immunization event was not carried out for some reason
